http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/telangana/Coaching-for-physically-challenged/article13981910.ece

The Disabled Welfare Department would offer coaching for the disabled persons to appear for recruitment examinations that would be conducted by the government.Those who want to attend coaching should be aged between 18 to 54 years and annual income should not be more than Rs. 2 lakh per annum.Selected candidates would be paid Rs. 15,000 for three months period in addition to Rs. 5,000 as coaching fee.Interested candidates can submit their applications before January 18 at the office of Assistant Director, Disabled Welfare, Sangareddy.